## ⛳ Completion signal — REQUIRED LAST LINE (run_claude_job.sh reads this for Steve's Telegram alert)

After all work and logging, the VERY LAST line of your output MUST be exactly one of:
- `ROUTINE_COMPLETE` — the agent verified the figures and wrote its report (a clean "all current" cycle IS complete; a cycle that FOUND stale cites is also complete — the finding is the product).
- `ROUTINE_INCOMPLETE: <one-line reason>` — the agent failed/returned blocked or partial (e.g. could not verify a figure / no web access), or you could not run the agent at all.

Output nothing after that line.
